sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant BlogsUI as Blogs Dashboard + ArticleForm
    participant BlogAPI as /api/blogs endpoints
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    Admin->>BlogsUI: Open /dashboard/blogs
    BlogsUI->>BlogAPI: GET /api/blogs?page=1
    BlogAPI->>DB: Query LAB_ARTICLE records
    DB-->>BlogAPI: Articles list
    BlogAPI-->>BlogsUI: List payload
    BlogsUI-->>Admin: Render article table/cards

    Admin->>BlogsUI: Create or edit article
    BlogsUI->>BlogAPI: POST or PATCH /api/blogs
    BlogAPI->>DB: Insert or update article row
    DB-->>BlogAPI: Persisted row
    opt status=published
        BlogAPI->>BlogAPI: Trigger subscriber campaign workflow
        Note over BlogAPI,DB: Full mail broadcast flow in publish_newsletter_broadcast_sequence.mmd
    end
    BlogAPI-->>BlogsUI: Success response
    BlogsUI->>BlogAPI: GET /api/blogs (refresh)
    BlogAPI-->>BlogsUI: Updated list

    Admin->>BlogsUI: Delete article
    BlogsUI->>BlogAPI: DELETE /api/blogs/:id
    BlogAPI->>DB: Soft delete or hard delete row
    DB-->>BlogAPI: Delete result
    BlogAPI-->>BlogsUI: Success
